<p class="">Will the hon. Member tell me, out of his great experience and expert knowledge, before leaving this point of economics, how a man with a wife and two children on £5 a week can afford to pay 25s. a week rent for a council house?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
