<p class="">Of course, in London a man with a wife and two children would not pay 25s. a week for an L.C.C. flat. Our rents do not go as high as that for two-roomed flats, and on some other occasion I will give the hon. Gentleman full details if he likes.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
