<p class="">I should like the hon. Gentleman to answer my question if he can.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7ddcb999-a8c0-4875-8819-7e58df590dc9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
