    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it not rather a humanitarian question?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bd56eb6f-c48b-44f1-9a35-d7311b884efe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
