<p class="">If it is wrong for the agricultural worker to live in a tied house so that he can be near to his work, it must equally be wrong for any Minister of the Crown, any policeman, any stationmaster and many resident hospital doctors to live in tied houses.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
