        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7b7834ad-8355-4a2e-968c-4032dce6ce6d">
                Mr. Mott-Radclyffe
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7b7834ad-8355-4a2e-968c-4032dce6ce6d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-03-16/debates/2aa8a3fb-3ca5-4675-a9b5-5071ad2f9d44/HousingBill#contribution-7b7834ad-8355-4a2e-968c-4032dce6ce6d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does the hon. Member mean to apply that principle to the Forestry Commission's cottages, the <span id="2214" class="column-number" data-column-number="2214"></span> Coal Board's cottages, and public corporations' houses?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7b7834ad-8355-4a2e-968c-4032dce6ce6d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-03-16/debates/2aa8a3fb-3ca5-4675-a9b5-5071ad2f9d44/HousingBill#contribution-7b7834ad-8355-4a2e-968c-4032dce6ce6d">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
