<p class="">We understood that these services would not be a burden upon the rates.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-73076a02-ae49-4836-8b45-38052d3c0a5e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
